DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		FILTER(
			KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('narendra pizza'[order_date])),
			'narendra pizza'[order_date] < DATE(2015, 10, 16)
		)

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		CALCULATETABLE(
			VALUES('narendra pizza'[pizza_category]),
			KEEPFILTERS(__DS0FilterTable)
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(101, __DS0Core, 'narendra pizza'[pizza_category], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
	'narendra pizza'[pizza_category]

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"Chicken"}, 'narendra pizza'[pizza_category])

	VAR __DS0FilterTable2 = 
		FILTER(
			KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('narendra pizza'[order_date])),
			'narendra pizza'[order_date] < DATE(2015, 10, 16)
		)

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'narendra pizza'[order day],
			__DS0FilterTable,
			__DS0FilterTable2,
			"TotalOrders", 'narendra pizza'[TotalOrders]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(1001, __DS0Core, [TotalOrders], 0, 'narendra pizza'[order day], 1)

EVALUATE
	GROUPBY(
		__DS0Core,
		"MinTotalOrders", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [TotalOrders]),
		"MaxTotalOrders", MAXX(CURRENTGROUP(), [TotalOrders])
	)

EVALUATE
	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
	[TotalOrders] DESC, 'narendra pizza'[order day]
